r studying the high-redshift\nUniverse. We obtain a strong lower limit on the total mass of \\emph{El Gordo},\n$\\gtrsim1.7\\times10^{15}M_{\\odot}$ from the SL regime alone, suggesting a total\nmass of, roughly, $M_{200}\\sim2.3\\times10^{15}M_{\\odot}$. Our results should be\nrevisited when additional spectroscopic and \\emph{HST} imaging data are\navailable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Apr 2013 20:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 May 2013 12:40:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-09"}
