 and a black hole spin. We\nhave also computed the QPOs from the oscillating relativistic torus.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Apr 2013 10:41:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 May 2013 06:19:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 17 Nov 2013 14:57:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-04"}
